Worley is a leading global provider of professional project and asset services in the energy, chemicals and resources sectors. We cover the full project life cycle from guiding our customers with pioneering projects to finding innovative ways of sustaining and enhancing their existing assets. Our comprehensive geographic presence enables us to leverage global expertise and deliver innovative solutions locally, to meet our customers' needs. Through OneWay™ our enterprise-wide integrity management framework, we establish corporate expectations for Zero Harm to people, assets and no environmental incidents, delivering predictable, consistent outcomes across the entire business. OneWay underpins all our business activities and starts with a personal commitment from everyone who works for us, regardless of location or role. Click here to find out more about Worley.